description:
Subscribe for More Videos!
This is the Christmas Story made out of lego. It is straight out of the message bible! If you would like to use this please let me know and I could even arrange to send it to you in a format you want. I hope you enjoyed this video and was inspired by this story!

Music is by the amazing Steven Sharp Nelson (The Piano Guys). The music in this video is mainly from there Christmas Cello Album! Check them out at http://thepianoguys.com/


If you liked this video you can watch my David and Goliath in lego!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=29LisuzEGzk

or

You can watch the Easter Story in Lego!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=goZvjl-4oAY
